But we don't need to say too much

549
00:46:19,300 --> 00:46:21,960
The stairs are behind
us, high and dark

550
00:46:22,040 --> 00:46:26,080
As we walk towards the quiet park

551
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:32,620
Twilight on the metal stairs

552
00:46:33,180 --> 00:46:35,580
Leaving the roof behind

553
00:46:35,660 --> 00:46:38,660
We carry the golden hour

554
00:46:40,120 --> 00:46:41,920
In our mind

555
00:46:43,760 --> 00:46:56,960
The metal stairs fade in the dark

556
00:46:57,040 --> 00:47:00,780
We step out past the streetlamp mark

557
00:47:01,220 --> 00:47:03,820
Blue hour is complete

558
00:47:04,480 --> 00:47:07,820
Back on the quiet street
